## Proposed Changes

### Component 1: Python Package Setup
We will bundle the inference engine code from the local `./tirex-2` directory into `forecastagent` to make it fully self-contained. This eliminates the need for users to compile Triton or have local submodules. We will also include monkeypatches that resolve compilation and Triton dependency errors on Windows out of the box.

