### Component 3: GitHub Automation Script

#### [NEW] [scripts/create_github_repo.py](file:///c:/Users/wei.liu/Documents/ForecastAgent/scripts/create_github_repo.py)
A utility script that:
- Prompts for a GitHub Personal Access Token (PAT).
